tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE financial_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    company_name VARCHAR,
    stock_price DECIMAL,
    stock_volume INT,
    trade_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE financial_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  date DATE,
  stock_symbol VARCHAR(10),
  closing_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
  volume INT
);

CREATE TABLE regression_analysis (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  analysis_date DATE,
  regression_coefficient DECIMAL(10, 2),
  p_value DECIMAL(10, 2),
  accuracy DECIMAL(5, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE FinancialData (
	id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	date DATE,
	stock_symbol VARCHAR,
	closing_price DECIMAL,
	volume INT
);

CREATE TABLE financial_data (
	financial_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	stock_symbol VARCHAR(255),
	date DATE,
	closing_price DECIMAL(10,2),
	volume INT
)

CREATE TABLE regression_models (
	model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	model_name VARCHAR(255),
	model_type VARCHAR(100),
	training_data_table VARCHAR(255),
	prediction_result_table VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE model_parameters (
	parameter_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	model_id INT,
	parameter_name VARCHAR(255),
	parameter_value FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE prediction_results (
	prediction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	model_id INT,
	date DATE,
	predicted_price DECIMAL(10,2),
	confidence_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE financial_data (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    stock_symbol VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,
    date DATE NOT NULL,
    closing_price DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    opening_price DECIMAL NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE regression_results (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    stock_symbol VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,
    prediction DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    actual_value DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    prediction_date DATE NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE market_trends (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    trend_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    trend_description TEXT,
    trend_start_date DATE NOT NULL,
    trend_end_date DATE NOT NULL
);
